<%= partial 'common/inner-header' %>

<section class="container">
  <h2>Gift List</h2>

  <p>We’re going to make our dream trip in Spring/Summer 2016 and travel down the West Coast of America - <strong>can you help us fulfil our dream?</strong></p>

  <p>Fuelled by our love for American comedies (Portlandia, Park and Recs &amp; Arrested Development), Sam’s mecca of Silicon Valley and Sasha’s childhood affection for 80s Americana what better reason than our honeymoon to make a pilgrimage to the US of A. Some songs on our wedding day pay homage to these spaces and places. Keep your ears open.</p>


  <div class="honeymoon-items">
    <% data.gifts.list.each do |g| %>
    <div class="a-third">
      <div class="honeymoon-item">
        <div class="honeymoon-item__bg">
          <h3 class="honeymoon-item__title"><%= g.title %></h3>
        </div>
        <h4 class="honeymoon-item__price" data-price="<%= g.pricePennies %>">£<%= g.priceText %></h4>
        <p class="honeymoon-item__description"><%= g.description %></p>
        <button type="button" class="honeymoon-item__buy">Buy this</button>
      </div>
    </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>

  <div class="modal-overlay"></div>
  <div class="modal">
    <a href="#" class="close-modal"></a>

    <header class="modal__header">
      <h2>Tickets for Red Sox Game</h2>
    </header>

    <form action="<%= site_url %>/charge" method="POST" class="payment-form">

      <div class="form-field">
        <label>From</label>
        <input type="text" name="from">
      </div>

      <div class="form-field">
        <label>Email</label>
        <input type="email" name="email" class="payment-form__email">
      </div>

      <div class="form-field">
        <label>Name <span class="side-note">(as it appears on card)</span></label>
        <input type="text" name="name" class="stripe-name">
      </div>

      <div class="payment-errors"></div>

      <div class="form-field">
        <label>Card Number</label>
        <input type="text" name="number" class="stripe-number" placeholder="•••• •••• •••• ••••">
      </div>

      <div class="form-field form-field--half-width payment-form__exp-date">
        <label>Expiry Date</label>
        <input type="text" name="expiry_date" class="stripe-exp-date" placeholder="•• / ••">
      </div>

      <div class="form-field form-field--half-width payment-form__cvc">
        <label>CVC</label>
        <input type="text" name="cvc" class="stripe-cvc" placeholder="•••" data-numeric>
      </div>

      <input type="hidden" name="price" value="" class="payment-form__price">
      <input type="hidden" name="item" value="" class="payment-form__item">

      <button type="submit" class="payment-form__button">
        <span class="button-text">Pay £80.00</span>
        <span class="loading"></span>
      </button>

      <a target="_blank" href="http://stripe.com" class="powered-by-stripe">
        <img src="/images/stripe.png" alt="Powered by Stripe">
      </a>
    </form>

    <div class="success-payment">
      <img src="/images/us.png" alt="Thanks">
      <h3>Thankyou so much!</h3>
      <p>You will receive a receipt to your email address shortly.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

</section>